他知道我讨厌香肠和橄榄口味...
He knows I hate sausage and olives...

164
00:10:13,690 --> 00:10:16,150
看你干的好事! 你这个小浑蛋!
Look what you did, you little jerk!

165
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:31,080
给我上楼
Get upstairs now.

166
00:10:31,250 --> 00:10:32,290
为什么?
Why?

167
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:34,170
你真是个衰鬼
You're such a disease.

168
00:10:34,420 --> 00:10:36,760
- 闭上你的嘴巴 - 凯文 上楼去!
-  Shut up! -  Kevin, upstairs!

169
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:39,130
- 说晚安 凯文 - 晚安 凯文
-  Say good night, Kevin. -  "Good night, Kevin."

170
00:10:42,090 --> 00:10:43,970
为什么我待遇这么差
Why do I get treated like scum?

171
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:46,770
对不起 家里乱糟糟的
I'm sorry. This house is just crazy.

172
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:49,230
家里又多了些孩子
We've got all these extra kids running around.

173
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:52,610
我哥哥也从俄亥俄州过来了 真是乱上加乱
My brother's in from Ohio. It's nuts.

174
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:55,230
怎么不多送些起司披萨来?
How come you didn't bring more cheese pizzas?

175
00:10:56,190 --> 00:10:58,490
- 这么多小费 - 谢谢
-  Nice tip. Thanks. -  Thanks.

176
00:10:58,650 --> 00:10:59,900
亲朋好友都来过节啦?
Having a reunion?

177
00:11:00,070 --> 00:11:04,410
我先生的哥哥被调到巴黎工作 孩子们还留在这里上学
My husband's brother transferred to Paris. His kids are still here.

178
00:11:04,660 --> 00:11:07,290
他想他家人了 所以叫我们全都去巴黎过节
He missed the family, so he invited us to Paris...

179
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:08,660
我们就可以全在一起了
...so we'll be together.

180
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:12,590
- 你们要去巴黎吗? - 是的 明天就动身
-  You're taking a trip to Paris? -  Yes, we leave tomorrow morning.

181
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:14,830
太好了 真是太好了
Excellent. Excellent.

182
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:18,090
真是抱歉 这孩子闹别扭
If you'll excuse me, this one's a little out of sorts.

183
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:21,010
不用招呼我 我今天已经跟你丈夫聊过了
Don't worry about me. I spoke to your husband.

184
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:26,050
也不用担心你家了 有我们呢
And don't worry about your home. It's in good hands.

185
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:32,100
这房子里有15个人 就是你老惹麻烦
Fifteen people in this house, and only you have to make trouble.

186
00:11:32,310 --> 00:11:33,690
我是个受气包
I'm getting dumped on.

187
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:36,690
你是个淘气包 好了 上楼去吧
You're the only one acting up. Now get upstairs.

188
00:11:36,940 --> 00:11:39,230
我不是已经在楼上了吗 白痴
I am upstairs, dummy!

189
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:41,610
还上三楼呀?
The third floor?

190
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:43,990
- 上去吧 - 上面太恐怖了
-  Go. -  It's scary up there.

191
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,070
富勒马上就会上去的
Fuller'll be up in a while.

192
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:49,330
我不要和他一起睡 他尿床
I don't want to sleep with Fuller. He wets the bed.

193
00:11:49,540 --> 00:11:51,750
他会把我浇湿 我知道他会
He'll pee all over me. I know it.

194
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,750
我让他睡别的地方
We'll put him somewhere else.

195
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,380
对不起
I'm sorry.

196
00:11:56,710 --> 00:11:59,000
时间不早了 快上楼睡吧
It's too late. Get upstairs.

197
00:12:02,170 --> 00:12:04,090
家里的每个人都讨厌我!
Everyone in this family hates me!

198
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:06,470
那你应该叫圣诞老人帮你换个新家
Then ask Santa for a new family.

199
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:10,140
我才不要什么新家呢! 我什么家都不要! 家太让人讨厌了
I don't want a new family. I don't want any family. Families suck!

200
00:12:10,350 --> 00:12:13,480
就待在上面吧! 今天晚上我再也不要看见你了
Stay up there. I don't want to see you again tonight.

201
00:12:13,690 --> 00:12:16,190
我以后一辈子也不想再看见你了
I don't want to see you for the rest of my life.

202
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:18,860
还有其他人我也都不想再看到
I don't want to see anybody else either.

203
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:21,070
你最好不是认真的
I hope you don't mean that.

204
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:25,160
要是明天早上醒来家没了 你会伤心的
You'd feel pretty sad if you woke up and didn't have a family.

205
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:27,370
不 我才不会
No, I wouldn't.

206
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:30,160
那你再讲一次啊 说不定真会发生呢
Then say it again. Maybe it'll happen.

207
00:12:30,370 --> 00:12:33,580
我想永远再也不要看见你们这些讨厌鬼!
I hope I never see any of you jerks again!

208
00:12:54,310 --> 00:12:57,440
我希望他们全都消失
I wish they would all just disappear.

209
00:13:54,330 --> 00:13:57,660
- 人在哪? - 谁知道? 她说了8点整的
-  Where are they? -  I don't know. She said 8 sharp.

210
00:14:06,130 --> 00:14:07,590
彼得!
Peter!

211
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:11,470
- 睡过头了! - 睡过头了!
-  We slept in! -  We slept in!

212
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:31,200
嗨 我是米奇·墨菲 住在对面
Hi, I'm Mitch Murphy. I live across the street.

213
00:14:31,410 --> 00:14:33,200
你们要出远门吗?
You guys going out of town?

214
00:14:33,450 --> 00:14:34,780
我们要去佛罗里达
We're going to Florida.

215
00:14:34,990 --> 00:14:38,620
其实我们得先去密苏里接我奶奶
Well, first we're going to Missouri to pick up my grandma.

216
00:14:38,830 --> 00:14:41,330
麦卡利斯特先生全家是要去法国
You know the McCallisters are going to France?

217
00:14:41,540 --> 00:14:42,920
那里冷吗?
Do you know if it's cold?

218
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:47,710
- 这些车费油吗? - 小子 不知道 闪开!
-  Do these vans get good mileage? -  Kid, I don't know. Hit the road!

219
00:14:51,390 --> 00:14:53,640
先点一下人头 然后叫他们全上车
Do a head count. Get everyone in the vans.

220
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:55,050
护照和飞机票在哪里?
Where are the passports?

221
00:14:55,310 --> 00:14:57,180
在微波炉里烘干
I put them in the microwave to dry.

222
00:14:57,430 --> 00:15:01,190
这车能跑多快? 是自排的吗?
How fast does this go? Does it have automatic transmission?

223
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:03,190
有四轮驱动吗?
Does it have 4- wheel drive?

224
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:07,280
我说过了 小子 别烦我 快闪!
Look, I told you before, kid. Don't bother me. Now, beat it!

225
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:20,960
在车前面排好队!
Line up in front of the van.

226
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:24,880
排好了 别说话!
Line up and shut up!

227
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:27,880
安静点! 我要点人数了
Shut up! I gotta take a head count.

228
00:15:28,340 --> 00:15:29,380
1 2 3...
One, two, three...

229
00:15:29,590 --> 00:15:31,970
11 92 12
Eleven, 92, 12....

230
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,550
巴兹 少耍白痴了
Buzz, don't be a moron.

231
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:37,680
6 7 8...
Six, seven, eight...

232
00:15:37,890 --> 00:15:40,480
9 10 11
...nine, 10, 11.

233
00:15:40,770 --> 00:15:44,520
好了 一半人上那辆车 另一半上这辆车
Okay, half in this van, half in this one. Let's go.

234
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:48,480
旅途愉快! 从法国带点东西回来给我
Have a good trip. Bring me back something French.

235
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:55,030
我们绝对赶不上飞机了 剩下不到45分钟了
There's no way we'll make this plane. It leaves in 45 minutes.

236
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:56,490
多往好处想
Think positive!

237
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:58,620
想有什么用 还是实际点
You be positive. I'll be realistic.

238
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:02,390
你家的电线修好了
Ma'am. Ma'am. Excuse me, your power is fixed...

239
00:16:02,580 --> 00:16:06,210
但是你家的电话线绕得乱七八糟的 要好几天才能整理好
...but the phones are a mess. It'll take a couple of days to fix.

240
00:16:06,380 --> 00:16:08,800
- 特别是在过节期间 - 谢谢
-  Especially around the holidays. -  Thanks.

241
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,340
点过人数没有?
Did you count heads?

242
00:16:11,130 --> 00:16:12,340
11个 包括我
Eleven, including me.

243
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:15,730
5个男孩 6个女孩 家长有4个 2个司机
Five boys, six girls, four parents, two drivers,

244
00:16:15,730 --> 00:16:17,330
还有梨树上的一只鹌鹑
and a partridge in a pear tree.

245
00:16:52,970 --> 00:16:54,300
飞机等一下!
Hold the plane!

246
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:56,430
- 我们错过班机了吗? - 刚好赶上
-  Did we miss it? -  You just made it.

247
00:16:58,300 --> 00:17:01,310
经济舱座位随便坐
Single seats only in coach. Take whatever's free.

248
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:04,270
我要坐窗边!
I get a window seat!

249
00:17:07,270 --> 00:17:10,900
- 孩子们到经济舱 我们坐这 - 4号A座 B座
-  Kids are in coach, we're first class. -  Seats Four A and B.

250
00:17:11,110 --> 00:17:13,570
4号A座 B座 把大衣给我吧
Four A and B. I'll take your coats.

251
00:17:14,990 --> 00:17:17,200
- 请系好安全带 - 给我来杯香槟
-  Fasten your seat belts. -  Champagne, please.

252
00:17:17,410 --> 00:17:19,530
- 是免费的吧? - 是的 先生
-  It's free, isn't it? -  Oh, yes.

253
00:17:20,450 --> 00:17:21,580
我们还好赶上了
We made it.

254
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:25,660
真不敢相信 最好没有忘了什么东西
Do you believe it? Hope we didn't forget anything.

255
00:18:46,450 --> 00:18:47,540
妈?
Mom?

256
00:18:53,090 --> 00:18:54,880
谢谢
Thank you.

257
00:18:55,090 --> 00:18:58,420
- 这是真的 真水晶做的 - 所以呢?
-  That's real. That's real crystal. -  Yeah, so?

258
00:18:58,630 --> 00:19:01,550
- 快放进你的皮包里 - 这样不行 法兰克
-  Put them in your purse. -  Frank, I can't do that.

259
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:04,510
快放进你的皮包里
Just... Put them in your purse!

260
00:19:04,890 --> 00:19:07,390
好的 倒满 倒满
Yeah. Fill it up. Fill it up.

261
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:08,930
请倒满
Fill it up, please.

262
00:19:09,890 --> 00:19:10,890
谢谢
Thank you.

263
00:19:11,060 --> 00:19:14,650
孩子们坐经济舱 我们坐头等舱 你不会觉得不好意思吗?
Don't you feel like a heel, flying first class with the kids in coach?

264
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:16,230
孩子们很好啊
No. The kids are fine.

265
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,870
我小的时候唯一一次的旅行
The only time I ever flew as a kid

266
00:19:17,870 --> 00:19:20,740
坐的还是家庭旅行车 当然不是去法国
was in the station wagon, not to France.

267
00:19:21,030 --> 00:19:23,910
我们那时候常去罗拉婶婶和亚瑟叔叔家玩
We had to go to Aunt Laura and Uncle Arthur's.

268
00:19:24,410 --> 00:19:27,290
孩子们都很好 他们在享受生活 都很愉快
Kids are okay. They're having the time of their lives.

269
00:19:28,410 --> 00:19:30,000
有人吗?
Hello?

270
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:32,920
妈
Mom?

271
00:19:35,290 --> 00:19:36,750
爸?
Dad?

272
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:43,590
妈? 爸?
Mom? Dad?

273
00:19:45,470 --> 00:19:47,510
你们都去哪里了?
Where are you guys?

274
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:49,810
巴兹?
Buzz?

275
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,230
巴兹?
Buzz?

276
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:58,610
巴兹?
Buzz?

277
00:20:02,990 --> 00:20:04,240
梅根?
Megan?

278
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:06,120
喂!
Hello?

279
00:20:06,950 --> 00:20:08,830
喂!
Hello?

280
00:20:08,990 --> 00:20:10,290
罗德?
Rod?

281
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:11,950
法兰克叔叔?
Uncle Frank?

282
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:14,830
法兰克叔叔 是开玩笑吗?
Uncle Frank, is this a joke?

283
00:20:16,340 --> 00:20:19,550
梅根? 琳妮?
Megan? Linnie?

284
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:23,880
你们在玩吧?
Is this a joke?

285
00:20:47,530 --> 00:20:49,280
是我乱想
It's only my imagination.

286
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:51,490
就是我乱想的
Only my imagination.

287
00:21:08,930 --> 00:21:12,060
车子还在这里 他们没有去机场啊
The cars are still here. They didn't go to the airport!

288
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:33,580
我让全家人消失了!
I made my family disappear.

289
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:36,790
"你完全无法照顾自己"
You're completely helpless.

290
00:21:37,040 --> 00:21:41,850
凯文... 你就是法语中说的那种"无能之辈"
You know, Kevin, you're what the French call les incompetents.

291
00:21:42,090 --> 00:21:45,050
"凯文 我要把你喂给我的大蜘蛛"
Kevin, I'm going to feed you to my tarantula.

292
00:21:45,220 --> 00:21:48,050
"凯文 你真是个衰鬼"
Kevin, you are such a disease.

293
00:21:48,260 --> 00:21:53,220
"这房子里有15个人 就是你老惹麻烦"
There are 15 people, and you're the only one who has to make trouble.

294
00:21:53,560 --> 00:21:57,060
"瞧你干的好事 你这个小浑蛋!"
Look what you did, you little jerk!

295
00:22:00,610 --> 00:22:04,190
我让全家人消失了!
I made my family disappear.

296
00:22:18,250 --> 00:22:20,080
我自由了
I'm free!

297
00:22:40,190 --> 00:22:43,400
都不穿衣服 真恶心!
No clothes on anybody. Sickening!

298
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:48,120
酷! 鞭炮! 留着以后玩
Cool! Firecrackers! I'll save these for later.

299
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:51,110
巴兹 我在翻你的东西
Buzz, I'm going through all your private stuff.

300
00:22:51,370 --> 00:22:53,910
还不快出来收拾我!
You better come out and pound me!

301
00:22:57,910 --> 00:23:00,960
巴兹的女朋友 好恶
Buzz, your girlfriend! Woof!

302
00:23:38,050 --> 00:23:40,170
邪恶天使

303
00:23:49,970 --> 00:23:51,340
谁呀?
Who is it?

304
00:23:55,010 --> 00:23:57,960
是我 小蛇 东西到手了
It's me, Snakes. I got the stuff.

305
00:23:58,180 --> 00:24:00,930
放在台阶上 然后滚蛋
Leave it on the doorstep and get the hell out.

306
00:24:01,180 --> 00:24:04,270
可以 强尼 但钱呢?
All right, Johnny, but what about my money?

307
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:05,520
要钱吗?
What money?

308
00:24:05,730 --> 00:24:07,980
老大说有我的一份
A.C. said you had some dough for me.

309
00:24:08,190 --> 00:24:11,110
是吗? 该给多少?
Is that a fact? How much do I owe you?

310
00:24:11,320 --> 00:24:13,240
老大说过 十分之一
A.C. said 10 percent.

311
00:24:14,410 --> 00:24:16,870
可惜老大说的不算了
Too bad A.C. ain't in charge no more.

312
00:24:17,740 --> 00:24:20,040
我边吃零食边看烂电影
Guys, I'm eating junk and watching rubbish!

313
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:22,790
还不快出来阻止我!
You better come out and stop me!

314
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:25,120
他洗完澡后会打电话给你的
He'll call you when he gets out.

315
00:24:26,670 --> 00:24:28,040
嘿
Hey.

316
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:30,300
告诉你要给你什么
I'll tell you what I'll give you.

317
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:34,220
我数十下...
I'm gonna give you to the count of 10...

318
00:24:34,930 --> 00:24:37,220
你这个杂种...
...to get your ugly, yellow...

319
00:24:37,430 --> 00:24:39,600
赶快滚蛋
...no- good keister off my property...

320
00:24:39,810 --> 00:24:41,810
不然就请你吃子弹
...before I pump your guts full of lead.

321
00:24:42,020 --> 00:24:44,800
好好 对不起 我马上走
All right, I'm sorry. I'm going.

322
00:24:44,900 --> 00:24:47,100
1 2...10!
One, two...10.

323
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:04,750
不用找了 畜生!
Keep the change, you filthy animal.

324
00:25:06,670 --> 00:25:08,000
妈!
Mom!

325
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,640
怎么了?
What's the matter?

326
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:23,270
亲爱的?
Honey?

327
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:28,210
- 我有种怪怪的感觉 - 是什么呢?
-  I have a terrible feeling. -  About what?

328
00:25:29,690 --> 00:25:31,270
好像有什么事我们没做
That we didn't do something.

329
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:34,780
你有这感觉是因为我们走得太急了
You feel that way because we left in a hurry.

330
00:25:34,950 --> 00:25:38,260
- 我们该做的都做了 - 我关咖啡壶了吗?
-  We took care of everything. -  Did I turn off the coffee?

331
00:25:38,570 --> 00:25:39,780
没有
No.

332
00:25:39,950 --> 00:25:41,080
是我关的
I did.

333
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:42,700
你有没有锁门?
Did you lock up?

334
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:45,290
锁了
Yeah.

335
00:25:46,620 --> 00:25:48,000
车库门关了吗?
Did you close the garage?

336
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,090
这个我没关
That's it.

337
00:25:51,290 --> 00:25:53,710
我把车库门忘了 就这一件事
I forgot to close the garage. That's it.

338
00:25:59,470 --> 00:26:01,350
不 不是这件事
No, that's not it.

339
00:26:03,390 --> 00:26:05,100
我们还会忘记什么事呢?
What else could we be forgetting?

340
00:26:09,020 --> 00:26:10,060
是凯文!
Kevin!

341
00:26:53,770 --> 00:26:56,940
机长能做的都做了 你家的电话就是不通
The captain's doing all he can. Your phones are out of order.

342
00:26:57,150 --> 00:26:59,610
飞机一落地我们就打电话 我想不会有什么事的
We'll call when we land. I'm sure it's okay.

343
00:27:01,570 --> 00:27:03,570
真可怕 太可怕了
Horrible. Horrible.

344
00:27:03,910 --> 00:27:05,200
太可怕了
Just horrible.

345
00:27:05,620 --> 00:27:08,160
我们怎么会这样呢? 怎么会忘记他了呢?
How could we do this? We forgot him.

346
00:27:08,370 --> 00:27:10,660
我们没忘记他 就是没点对人数
We didn't forget him, we just miscounted.

347
00:27:11,750 --> 00:27:14,210
我算是怎样的母亲啊?
What kind of mother am I?

348
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:17,880
你听了也许会好过点 我连我的眼镜都忘记带了
If it makes you feel any better, I forgot my reading glasses.

349
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:25,470
光这一条街上 就有五户人家出去度假
Five families gone on one block alone.

350
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:28,640
都是他们亲口跟我说的
They all told me from their own mouths.

351
00:27:28,890 --> 00:27:30,390
真是天赐良机
It's almost too easy.

352
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:31,980
我们看看
Check it out:

353
00:27:32,190 --> 00:27:34,230
所有家里没人的房子
All the houses with nobody home...

354
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:37,270
都装了灯光自动计时器
...have automatic timers on their lights.

355
00:27:37,650 --> 00:27:40,940
但是我把所有的数字都搞到手了 看这个...
But I got it all figured out. Watch this.

356
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:47,120
664号灯马上...
Number 664 will be going on right about...

357
00:27:48,450 --> 00:27:49,700
就要亮!
...now.

358
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:52,670
等等 等等
Wait, wait, wait.

359
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:56,540
672号...
Number 672...

360
00:27:57,550 --> 00:28:00,090
现在亮!
...right now.

361
00:28:02,430 --> 00:28:03,510
等等 等等
Wait a minute.

362
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:06,680
671号...
671...

363
00:28:06,850 --> 00:28:07,930
亮!
...now.

364
00:28:10,430 --> 00:28:13,940
就是这一家 马文 是个金库
And that's the one, Marvin. That's the silver tuna.

365
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,650
真的搞大了
It's very G.

366
00:28:16,310 --> 00:28:18,730
大吧 啊?
Very G, huh? It's loaded.

367
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:21,190
屋里有好多高级货
It's got lots of top- flight goods.

368
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:24,740
- 有音响 录影机 - 玩具
-  Stereos, VCRs... -  Toys?

369
00:28:24,950 --> 00:28:27,530
可能有些精品珠宝首饰
Probably looking at some very fine jewelry.

370
00:28:27,950 --> 00:28:29,330
或许还有现钞
Possible cash horde.

371
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:32,580
有价证券什么的
Odd marketable securities.

372
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:35,540
谁知道呢 反正是个金库
Who knows? It's a gem.

373
00:28:36,330 --> 00:28:38,290
拿好你的铁橇
Grab your crowbar.

374
00:28:39,300 --> 00:28:40,960
铁橇真好用
Crowbars up.

375
00:29:40,150 --> 00:29:41,690
走哪边?
Which way?

376
00:29:41,860 --> 00:29:44,190
我们绕到后面到地下室去
We'll go around back, down the basement.

377
00:30:05,050 --> 00:30:07,840
- 你不是说他们都走了吗? - 他们是今天早上走的
-  You said they were gone. -  They were gonna leave today.

378
00:30:08,050 --> 00:30:09,680
快离开这吧
Let's get out of here.

379
00:30:46,130 --> 00:30:48,470
我们得用一下电话
We have to use the phone, please.

380
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:52,010
事情很急 我们真的非常需要打这个电话
It's an emergency. We really have to make a call.

381
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:54,720
拜托你! 我们的弟弟单独一个人在家里
Please! Our brother's home alone.

382
00:30:55,430 --> 00:30:57,220
把电话给我!
Give us the phone!

383
00:30:57,520 --> 00:30:58,730
对不起! 谢谢
I'm sorry. Thank you.

384
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:01,650
我打电话给警察 你去订一下回家的飞机票
I'm calling the police. Book us a flight home.

385
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:04,730
拿些零钱 打电话给你认识的人
Get change out of here. Call everybody you know.

386
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:09,110
这是我的通讯录 打电话给住在我们街上的人
Here's my address book. You and Frank call everyone on our street.

387
00:31:09,320 --> 00:31:11,110
可能有人能帮我们
Maybe somebody can help us.

388
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:14,700
喂? 她等一下回你电话
Hello? Hello? Oh, she'll have to call you back.

389
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:25,080
真可笑 只有胆小鬼才躲在床底下
This is ridiculous. Only a wimp would be hiding under a bed.

390
00:31:25,170 --> 00:31:29,170
我可不是胆小鬼 我现在是一家之主了
And I can't be a wimp. I'm the man of the house.

391
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:39,810
我不会再害怕了
Hey, I'm not afraid anymore!

392
00:31:40,850 --> 00:31:44,440
我说了 我不会害怕了!
I said, I'm not afraid anymore!

393
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:48,780
都听见了吗? 我再也不害怕了
Do you hear me? I'm not afraid anymore.

394
00:32:19,390 --> 00:32:20,680
警察局
Village police department.

395
00:32:20,850 --> 00:32:24,270
我现在在巴黎 我儿子现在独自在家
I'm calling from Paris. I have a son who's home alone.

396
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:29,570
所以我想请你们派个人 去我家看看
I'd like somebody to go there. Tell him that we're coming home to get him.

397
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:31,860
我帮你转到家庭危机解救中心
Okay, let me connect you with Family Crisis Intervention.

398
00:32:32,030 --> 00:32:33,360
不 这不是家庭纠纷
No it's not a family crisis.

399
00:32:33,530 --> 00:32:34,910
别挂
Hold on.

400
00:32:36,820 --> 00:32:40,200
拉瑞 接一下电话 有位神经质女士
Larry, can you pick up? There's some hyper lady on hold.

401
00:32:40,450 --> 00:32:42,790
- 几号线? 罗丝 - 2号
-  What line, Rose? -  Two.

402
00:32:43,460 --> 00:32:45,830
家庭危机解救中心 我是鲍沙警官
Family Crisis Intervention, Sergeant Balzak.

403
00:32:46,080 --> 00:32:48,920
我现在在巴黎 我儿子独自在家
I'm calling from Paris. I have a son who's home alone.

404
00:32:49,130 --> 00:32:53,800
这孩子家里有没有酒鬼 对他使用过暴力?
Has the child been involved in violence with a drunk family member?

405
00:32:54,010 --> 00:32:55,050
没有!
No!

406
00:32:55,340 --> 00:32:57,840
他在家发生过意外吗?
Has he been involved in a household accident?

407
00:32:58,050 --> 00:33:00,220
我不知道 希望他没有
I don't know. I hope not.

408
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:05,600
这孩子吃了有毒的东西 还是有什么硬东西卡在喉咙里了?
Has the child ingested any poison or is an object lodged in his throat?

409
00:33:05,850 --> 00:33:09,310
就是他单独一人在家里! 我想请个人到我家里...
No, he's home alone! I'd like somebody to go over to the house...

410
00:33:09,520 --> 00:33:11,320
看一下他有没有事!
...and see if he's all right.

411
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:16,030
你想让我们到你家去 就是看一下你的孩子?
You want us to go to your house, just to check on him.

412
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:17,320
没错!
Yes!

413
00:33:17,990 --> 00:33:19,570
那我帮你转接到警察局
Let me connect you to the police.

414
00:33:19,780 --> 00:33:21,240
刚刚就是他们把我转接到你这里的
They just transferred me.

415
00:33:21,410 --> 00:33:23,580
- 罗丝? 神经质在2线 - 等等
-  Rose! Hyper on 2. -  Hang on.

416
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:27,420
- 等一下 - 请等一下 别挂电话
-  Hold on, please. -  No, please don't hang up. Please!

417
00:33:28,250 --> 00:33:29,500
谁打通了?
Any luck?

418
00:33:29,670 --> 00:33:31,090
没有
No.

419
00:33:31,250 --> 00:33:33,920
- 我们一个人也没找到 - 莱丝莉?
-  I couldn't get anybody. -  Leslie?

420
00:33:34,130 --> 00:33:36,430
都是电话录音
Nothing but a bunch of answering machines.

421
00:33:38,590 --> 00:33:41,560
谁来接电话吧! 快接电话!
Somebody pick up. Pick up!

422
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,770
嗨 女士 又是你
Oh, hi, ma'am. It's you again.

423
00:33:43,930 --> 00:33:47,890
我现在在巴黎 我儿子现在独自在家
I'm calling from Paris. I have a son who's home alone, and I...

424
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:51,900
我们派一个警官到你家去看一下你儿子吧
We'll send a policeman over to your house to check on your son.

425
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:24,850
家里没有人 房子看起来很安全
There's no one home. The house looks secure.

426
00:34:25,060 --> 00:34:27,140
让他们再数数孩子
Tell them to count their kids again.

427
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:30,650
你不能换掉一个乘客或者...
You can't bump somebody or ask or... ?

428
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:32,690
我真的不能那么做
There's no way I can do that.

429
00:34:32,900 --> 00:34:34,980
你能不能问问看?
Isn't there a way if you ask somebody?

430
00:34:35,190 --> 00:34:36,690
这是一件紧急事件...
If you said it's an emergency...

431
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:38,150
可是我不能要求别人
I cannot ask them.

432
00:34:38,450 --> 00:34:40,700
他们要派警官到家里
A policeman's going over to the house.

433
00:34:40,910 --> 00:34:43,830
很好 可是机位全都满了
Well, that's a relief. Everything here is booked.

434
00:34:43,990 --> 00:34:45,080
没有去芝加哥的航班了吗?
Nothing to Chicago?

435
00:34:45,330 --> 00:34:48,500
芝加哥 纽约 那什维尔都满了
There's nothing to Chicago, New York, Nashville.

436
00:34:49,870 --> 00:34:53,000
- 私人飞机呢? - 对不起 我们没有这个业务
-  What about a private plane? -  Sorry. We don't do that.

437
00:34:53,250 --> 00:34:56,130
他们现在能做的就是 为我们订星期五早上的机位
The only thing is a booking for us on Friday morning.

438
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:58,840
星期五? 还有两天
Friday morn... That's two days away.

439
00:34:59,050 --> 00:35:01,350
孩子们都累了 你也累坏了
The kids are exhausted and so are you.

440
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:02,760
我们待在机场实在没有什么事能做了
There's nothing we can do.

441
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:07,970
我们先去罗伯家 在那里我们再给警察局打电话
I say we go over to Rob's, and that way we can call the police again.

442
00:35:08,270 --> 00:35:11,480
我不会离开机场的 除非坐上飞机
I'm not leaving here unless it's on an airplane.

443
00:35:11,690 --> 00:35:13,770
夫人 我们就是要尽一切可能帮助乘客
Madame, we are doing everything we can.

444
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:17,980
如果你留在机场候补 或许能碰上空位
If you want to stay at the airport, maybe we can get you on standby.

445
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:21,110
是有这种可能的
It is a possibility that a seat will open up.

446
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:24,660
- 这下行了吧 - 好吧 我等着
-  Is that okay? -  Yes. I'll wait.

447
00:35:30,410 --> 00:35:32,620
- 我会想你的 - 再见
-  Bye. I'll miss you, honey. -  Bye.

448
00:35:36,630 --> 00:35:38,380
别把你自己搞丢了
Don't you get lost.

449
00:35:39,970 --> 00:35:41,130
拜拜
Goodbye.

450
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:59,990
洗澡 擦香皂 全身上下都洗洗
I took a shower, washing every body part with actual soap.

451
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:02,110
手指缝...
Including all my major crevices...

452
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:04,740
脚指缝 还有肚脐
...between my toes and in my belly button...

453
00:36:04,990 --> 00:36:07,410
虽然从来没洗过 不过感觉还不错
...which I never did before but enjoyed.

454
00:36:07,910 --> 00:36:13,000
像大人那样用洗发精还有润发乳洗头
I washed my hair with adult formula shampoo and used cream rinse.

455
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:17,250
好像没有牙刷了 一会儿出去买一枝
I can't find my toothbrush, so I'll pick one up today.

456
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,590
没什么事了 还满像样子的嘛
Other than that, I'm in good shape.

457
00:37:10,220 --> 00:37:13,480
好耶! 巴兹存的零用钱
All right! Buzz's life savings.

458
00:37:40,290 --> 00:37:42,920
我还以为墨菲全家都去佛罗里达了
I thought the Murphys went to Florida.

459
00:37:59,190 --> 00:38:02,230
你可真是天下名偷
You're one of the great cat burglars of the world.

460
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:05,110
你能不能小声一点?
You think you can keep it down a little in there?

461
00:38:05,780 --> 00:38:09,530
家中无人 有事请留话
You've reached the Murphys. Please leave a message after the beep.

462
00:38:10,410 --> 00:38:14,290
我是彼得·麦卡利斯特 现在在我哥巴黎的公寓里
This is Peter McCallister again. We're in Paris at my brother's.

463
00:38:14,540 --> 00:38:17,960
我现在把这里的电话号码留给你 国码是33
Let me give you the number here. The country code is 33.

464
00:38:18,170 --> 00:38:23,130
区码是14 电话号码是694876
The area code is 14 and the number is 694- 876...

465
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:25,340
- 嘿 哈利! - 干嘛?
-  Hey, Harry. -  Yeah?

466
00:38:25,590 --> 00:38:28,430
昨晚我们去的那家 是彼得的家吗?
That house we ran last night, was that the McCallister's?

467
00:38:28,590 --> 00:38:30,090
是啊
Yeah.

468
00:38:30,430 --> 00:38:33,760
- 打电话到巴黎给我 - 你说的对 他们早走了
-  Call me in Paris. -  You're right. They're gone.

469
00:38:37,180 --> 00:38:40,730
- 我就知道他们不在 - 今晚搞定那个金库
-  I knew they were. -  Silver tuna tonight.

470
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:51,200
能帮你什么吗?
How may I help you?

471
00:38:51,870 --> 00:38:55,160
这种牙刷是不是美国牙医协会认可的?
Is this toothbrush approved by the American Dental Association?

472
00:38:55,950 --> 00:38:57,500
不知道
Well, I don't know.

473
00:38:58,580 --> 00:39:02,000
- 上面没有说明 - 请你查一下好吗?
-  It doesn't say, hon. -  Can you please find out?

474
00:39:05,170 --> 00:39:06,880
- 贺伯! - 什么事?
-  Herb. -  Yeah?

475
00:39:07,090 --> 00:39:10,340
我这里有人对牙刷有疑问
I got a question here about a toothbrush.

476
00:39:16,930 --> 00:39:21,440
你知不知道这种牙刷有没有经过牙医协会认可?
Do you know, is this brush approved by the American Dental Association?

477
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,770
不知道
I don't know.

478
00:39:45,250 --> 00:39:47,670
到这来付钱
Oh, hon, you pay for that here.

479
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:51,630
等一下 你得付钱
Wait, you have to pay for that.

480
00:39:52,390 --> 00:39:55,470
孩子 孩子
Son! Son! Hey!

481
00:39:55,930 --> 00:39:58,390
吉米 快抓住那孩子
Jimmy, stop that boy!

482
00:40:02,810 --> 00:40:03,980
嘿!
Hey!

483
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:06,060
嘿!
Hey!

484
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:09,820
抓小偷!
Shoplifter!

485
00:40:13,660 --> 00:40:14,860
哎 小子!
Hey! Hey, kid!

486
00:40:21,870 --> 00:40:23,250
给我过来!
Come back here!

487
00:40:24,750 --> 00:40:26,420
给我站住!
Stop it, will you?

488
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:28,090
回来
Come here.

489
00:41:06,250 --> 00:41:08,130
我是罪犯
I'm a criminal.

490
00:41:35,450 --> 00:41:37,160
有什么好笑的?
What's so funny?

491
00:41:37,950 --> 00:41:39,240
笑什么?
What's so funny?

492
00:41:39,740 --> 00:41:40,870
你笑什么啊?
Why are you laughing?

493
00:41:44,160 --> 00:41:45,370
又犯老毛病了吧?
You did it again.

494
00:41:46,790 --> 00:41:48,250
又没关水了对吧?
You left the water running.

495
00:41:49,170 --> 00:41:51,590
你这是什么毛病? 我早跟你说过不要这样
Why do you do that? I told you not to do it.

496
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:54,170
- 这叫雁过留声人过留名 - 雁过留声人过留名
-  It's our calling card. -  Calling card.

497
00:41:54,380 --> 00:41:56,510
天下所有的大盗都要留下他们的标记
All the great ones leave their mark.

498
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,340
我们就是"水盗"
We're the Wet Bandits.

499
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:01,300
你有病你知不知道? 真的有病
You're sick, you know? You're really sick.

500
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:03,970
- 我没病 - 你有
-  I'm not sick. -  Yes, you are.

501
00:42:04,180 --> 00:42:05,390
这么搞就是有病
It's a sick thing to do.

502
00:42:12,190 --> 00:42:14,030
- 不许再这么搞了! - 不要教我怎么搞
-  We don't need that. -  Don't tell me...

503
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:16,110
我爱怎么搞就怎么搞
I can do it if I want to.

504
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:20,490
我没有病! 小心点!
It's not sick. Hey, watch out!

505
00:42:28,790 --> 00:42:30,120
嘿! 嘿!
Hey! Hey!

506
00:42:30,330 --> 00:42:32,290
走路得小心
You gotta watch out for traffic.

507
00:42:32,670 --> 00:42:34,590
- 对不起 - 气死人
