Allow me to introduce myself. Gus Polinski.

684
00:59:20,340 --> 00:59:22,550
中西部波卡音乐之王
Polka King of the Midwest?

685
00:59:25,810 --> 00:59:27,310
听说过肯诺夏舞者吗?
The Kenosha Kickers?

686
00:59:28,600 --> 00:59:29,940
- 嗨 - 你好
-  Hi there. -  Hi.

687
00:59:30,810 --> 00:59:34,190
没关系 我以为你能认出我们来
That's okay. I thought you might have recognized...

688
00:59:34,440 --> 00:59:37,900
几年前我出了几首曲子 轰动一时
I had a few hits a few years ago. That's why I just...

689
00:59:38,070 --> 00:59:39,320
"波卡 波卡 波卡"
"Polka, Polka, Polka"?

690
00:59:41,860 --> 00:59:44,290
没听过吗? 那么"双湖波卡"呢?
No? "Twin Lakes Polka"?

691
00:59:44,330 --> 00:59:45,910
还有"亚犸乎兹亚波卡"
"Yamahoozie Polka, "

692
00:59:45,910 --> 00:59:49,490
就是"亲亲我波卡"? 还有"旋转波卡"...
a.k.a. "Kiss Me Polka"? "Polka Twist"?

693
00:59:49,490 --> 00:59:50,830
这些都是歌曲吗?
These are songs?

694
00:59:51,040 --> 00:59:53,920
是的 我们这帮人相当受欢迎
Yeah. Yeah, we... Some fairly big hits for us.

695
00:59:54,170 --> 00:59:55,960
特别是在70年代早期
You know, in the early '70s.

696
00:59:56,170 --> 00:59:58,960
我们卖了623张唱片
Yeah, we sold about 623 copies of that.

697
00:59:59,170 --> 01:00:00,760
- 在芝加哥吗? - 不 在希波干市
-  In Chicago? -  No, Sheboygan.

698
01:00:00,970 --> 01:00:02,630
全市都轰动了
Very big in Sheboygan.

699
01:00:02,840 --> 01:00:04,340
你是说能帮我吗?
Did you say you could help?

700
01:00:04,510 --> 01:00:08,270
我在喃喃自语 我们的航班取消了...
Anyway, I'm rambling on here. Our flight was canceled...

701
01:00:08,470 --> 01:00:12,850
所以我们准备开车去 看到那个穿黄夹克上有标记的人吗?
...so we gotta drive. See the guy in the yellow jacket over there?

702
01:00:13,060 --> 01:00:16,480
是他租给我们一辆漂亮的大车 我们开着去密尔瓦基
He's gonna rent us a nice big van to drive to Milwaukee.

703
01:00:16,690 --> 01:00:20,030
我刚才听你说要去芝加哥?
Now, I heard you had some problems getting to Chicago?

704
01:00:20,400 --> 01:00:21,650
去看你的孩子还是什么?
To see your kid?

705
01:00:21,900 --> 01:00:25,870
我们走的时候把他忘在家里了
My son. He... We left, and he's there.

706
01:00:26,030 --> 01:00:29,660
你要是去芝加哥 我们很高兴可以开车送你去
If you have to get to Chicago, we'll gladly drive you.

707
01:00:29,870 --> 01:00:31,960
正好是去密瓦基的路上
It's on the way to Milwaukee.

708
01:00:32,460 --> 01:00:34,880
- 你们可以送我? - 当然要送
-  You'd give me a ride? -  Sure, why not?

709
01:00:35,080 --> 01:00:36,590
你还是早点回家看孩子吧
You gotta get home.

710
01:00:36,790 --> 01:00:39,800
- 坐车去芝加哥? - 现在是圣诞节嘛
-  A ride to Chicago? -  Sure, it's Christmastime.

711
01:00:40,420 --> 01:00:42,010
谢谢你! 噢 谢谢!
Thank you. Oh, thank you.

712
01:00:42,260 --> 01:00:44,380
你不介意和波卡流浪艺人一起坐车吧?
You don't mind going with polka bums?

713
01:00:44,590 --> 01:00:46,390
不 不介意
No, I'd love to.

714
01:01:08,910 --> 01:01:11,410
嘿 马文
Hey, Marv. Marv, Marv!

715
01:01:11,620 --> 01:01:13,460
看看
Look at this.

716
01:01:19,420 --> 01:01:23,010
我看我们是让这个小子骗了
I think we're getting scammed by a kindergartner.

717
01:01:53,370 --> 01:01:55,620
爸爸 过来帮帮忙好不好?
Dad, can you come here and help me?

718
01:02:00,380 --> 01:02:02,750
还记得那天我们见到的那个小孩吗?
Remember that kid we saw the other day?

719
01:02:03,720 --> 01:02:05,220
就住这
He lives here.

720
01:02:05,550 --> 01:02:08,010
那要是孩子在家 父母肯定也在家
If the kid's here, the parents got to be.

721
01:02:08,640 --> 01:02:10,010
他可是单独一人在家
He's home alone.

722
01:02:18,270 --> 01:02:20,400
你白痴啊! 你要晚上才来吗?
What? You want to come back tonight?

723
01:02:20,610 --> 01:02:21,980
这个孩子在这你也敢来?
Even with the kid here?

724
01:02:22,230 --> 01:02:24,360
我觉得不能这样搞
I don't think that's a good idea.

725
01:02:24,570 --> 01:02:27,280
就是这房子使我们决定要在这个街区动手的
That house is the reason we worked this block.

726
01:02:27,530 --> 01:02:29,780
自从我第一次看到这栋房子 我就想要
Ever since I saw that house, I wanted it.

727
01:02:30,200 --> 01:02:32,160
我们一步步来
Let's take it one step at a time.

728
01:02:32,370 --> 01:02:36,910
先把卡车给腾空了 再吃点饭 九点左右我们再回来
We'll unload the van, get a bite to eat, we'll come back about 9:00.

729
01:02:37,210 --> 01:02:38,420
九点左右
Nine o'clock.

730
01:02:38,620 --> 01:02:39,920
那时候天就黑了
This way it's dark.

731
01:02:40,500 --> 01:02:43,210
对啊 小孩子怕黑
Yeah, kids are scared of the dark.

732
01:02:43,420 --> 01:02:46,090
你也怕黑 你自己知道
You're afraid of the dark too. You know you are.

733
01:02:47,590 --> 01:02:48,930
我不怕黑
No, I'm not.

734
01:02:49,140 --> 01:02:51,010
- 你就是怕! - 不怕不怕不怕!
-  Yes, you are. -  Not, not, not.

735
01:02:51,220 --> 01:02:52,390
就是怕
You are so.

736
01:02:52,600 --> 01:02:54,600
妈妈 你在哪呢?
Mom, where are you?

737
01:03:09,320 --> 01:03:10,570
你会吹这个吗?
Do you play?

738
01:03:11,240 --> 01:03:14,580
要不要试试看? 来嘛 试试 试试
Do you want to try? Go ahead, try it. Try it!

739
01:03:27,900 --> 01:03:29,160
圣诞老人

740
01:03:42,310 --> 01:03:44,400
- 对不起 - 什么事?
-  Excuse me. -  Yeah?

741
01:03:46,070 --> 01:03:47,650
嘿 这双鞋真漂亮!
Hey, nice shoes.

742
01:03:48,110 --> 01:03:49,610
噢 谢谢
Oh, thanks.

743
01:03:49,820 --> 01:03:53,280
圣诞老人还在这吗? 我有重要的事要跟他说
Is he still here? It's really important that I see him.

744
01:03:54,080 --> 01:03:57,450
他正要上车呢 你要是跑快点还能赶上他
He's getting in his car. If you hurry, you can catch him.

745
01:03:58,830 --> 01:04:03,170
真该死! 居然在圣诞前夕 给圣诞老人开罚单
How low! Giving Kriss Kringle a parking ticket on Christmas Eve!

746
01:04:03,380 --> 01:04:05,960
那下次是什么? 难道还要给复活节兔子打狂犬病疫苗吗?
What's next, rabies shots for the Easter Bunny?

747
01:04:06,170 --> 01:04:07,670
圣诞老人 等一下
Santa, hold on.

748
01:04:10,010 --> 01:04:14,100
- 能耽误你一下吗? - 要快一点 圣诞老人快迟到了
-  Can I talk to you? -  Make it quick. Santa's running late.

749
01:04:14,140 --> 01:04:16,430
我知道你不是真的圣诞老人
I know you're not the real Santa Claus.

750
01:04:16,930 --> 01:04:20,390
你怎么会这样说? 我想知道为什么
What makes you say that? Just out of curiosity.

751
01:04:20,600 --> 01:04:24,100
- 我能明白是怎么回事了 - 是的
-  I'm old enough to know how it works. -  All right.

752
01:04:24,270 --> 01:04:26,310
但是我也知道你在为圣诞老人做事
But I also know you work for him.

753
01:04:26,650 --> 01:04:29,480
- 我想请你帮我传话给他 - 说吧
-  I'd like you to give him a message. -  Shoot.

754
01:04:29,940 --> 01:04:34,700
我是凯文·麦卡利斯特 住林肯大道671号 要电话号码吗?
Kevin McCallister, 671 Lincoln Blvd. Do you need the phone number?

755
01:04:35,030 --> 01:04:36,280
不用了
No, that's all right.

756
01:04:36,660 --> 01:04:38,410
这件事非常重要
This is extremely important.

757
01:04:38,660 --> 01:04:41,970
请你告诉圣诞老人 今年不要送礼物了
Please tell him instead of presents,

758
01:04:41,970 --> 01:04:43,670
就把我的全家人送回来就行了
I just want my family back.

759
01:04:44,210 --> 01:04:46,750
不要玩具 什么都不要 就要彼得 凯蒂
No toys. Nothing but Peter, Kate,

760
01:04:46,750 --> 01:04:48,630
巴兹 梅根 琳妮 杰夫
Buzz, Megan, Linnie and Jeff.

761
01:04:48,840 --> 01:04:50,880
还有我的婶婶和表兄弟姐妹们
And my aunt and my cousins.

762
01:04:51,130 --> 01:04:54,220
如果有时间的话 还有我的叔叔法兰克 好吗?
And if he has time, my Uncle Frank. Okay?

763
01:04:55,930 --> 01:04:57,140
好的
Okay.

764
01:04:58,010 --> 01:05:00,310
- 我会想办法的 - 谢谢
-  I'll see what I can do. -  Thanks.

765
01:05:00,520 --> 01:05:05,060
等等! 我的小矮人把剩下的棒棒糖给她的男朋友了
Wait. My elf took the last of the candy canes home to her boyfriend.

766
01:05:05,350 --> 01:05:07,150
- 没关系 - 不用 别傻了
-  That's okay. -  No, don't be silly.

767
01:05:07,360 --> 01:05:10,230
见到圣诞老人的人 一定要得到点东西
Everybody who sees Santa has gotta get something.

768
01:05:10,440 --> 01:05:14,570
在这儿 伸出你的小爪子 拿去
Here, hold out your little paw there. There you go.

769
01:05:15,070 --> 01:05:17,410
- 别吃多了 不然吃不下饭 - 不会的
-  Don't spoil your dinner. -  I won't.

770
01:05:17,830 --> 01:05:19,240
谢谢
Thanks.

771
01:05:30,460 --> 01:05:32,050
妈的
Son of a... !

772
01:08:29,430 --> 01:08:30,770
圣诞快乐
Merry Christmas.

773
01:08:33,350 --> 01:08:34,560
我可以坐下吗?
May I sit down?

774
01:08:45,950 --> 01:08:47,280
我的孙女在那上面
That's my granddaughter.

775
01:08:47,950 --> 01:08:49,870
那个红头发的小女孩
The little red- haired girl.

776
01:08:51,870 --> 01:08:54,620
她和你差不多大 你认识她吗?
She's about your age. You know her?

777
01:08:54,790 --> 01:08:55,920
不认识
No.

778
01:08:56,130 --> 01:08:59,170
你住我隔壁 是吧?
You live next to me, don't you?

779
01:08:59,380 --> 01:09:02,920
你见到我可以跟我打招呼 你不用害怕
You can say hello when you see me. You don't have to be afraid.

780
01:09:03,930 --> 01:09:08,890
城里有很多关于我的传言 但都不是真的 懂吗?
There's a lot of things going around about me, but none of it's true. Okay?

781
01:09:09,720 --> 01:09:11,720
- 你今年有当个乖孩子吗? - 我想有吧
-  You've been good this year? -  I think so.

782
01:09:12,390 --> 01:09:13,730
敢发誓吗?
You swear to it?

783
01:09:14,100 --> 01:09:15,150
不
No.

784
01:09:15,400 --> 01:09:19,980
只有你觉得自己不好 才会到这个地方来
Yeah. Well, this is the place to be if you're feeling bad about yourself.

785
01:09:20,400 --> 01:09:23,030
- 是吗? - 我是这么想的
-  It is? -  I think so.

786
01:09:23,240 --> 01:09:25,820
- 你觉得自己不好吗? - 没有
-  Are you feeling bad about yourself? -  No.

787
01:09:30,290 --> 01:09:35,580
最近我一直惹人厌 尽说些不该说的话
I've been kind of a pain lately. I said some things I shouldn't have.

788
01:09:35,620 --> 01:09:38,210
今年我的表现真的不太好
I really haven't been too good this year.

789
01:09:38,840 --> 01:09:39,880
是的
Yeah.

790
01:09:40,050 --> 01:09:43,300
我满难过的 我真的很爱我的家人
I'm kind of upset because I really like my family.

791
01:09:43,510 --> 01:09:48,430
尽管有时我嘴上说我不爱他们 我甚至心里想过我不爱他们
Even though sometimes I say I don't. Sometimes I even think I don't.

792
01:09:48,720 --> 01:09:51,470
- 你明白了吗? - 差不多吧
-  Do you get that? -  I think so.

793
01:09:51,930 --> 01:09:54,770
家家都有一本难念的经
How you feel about your family is a complicated thing.

794
01:09:55,020 --> 01:09:57,440
特别是和哥哥的关系
Especially with an older brother.

795
01:09:58,190 --> 01:10:00,520
内心深处虽然总是爱着他们
Deep down, you'll always love them.

796
01:10:00,730 --> 01:10:05,030
但却不知怎样去表现 于是就伤害了他们也伤害了自己
But you can forget that you love them. You can hurt them, they can hurt you.

797
01:10:05,240 --> 01:10:07,660
这跟年纪大小好像没有关系
And that's not just because you're young.

798
01:10:09,370 --> 01:10:12,080
你是不是想知道我到这里的真正原因?
You want to know the real reason why I'm here?

799
01:10:12,290 --> 01:10:13,540
是的
Sure.

800
01:10:14,000 --> 01:10:18,130
我是来听我孙女唱歌的 而今晚我是不能来的
I came to hear my granddaughter sing. I can't come hear her tonight.

801
01:10:18,380 --> 01:10:19,460
你有约会吗?
You have plans?

802
01:10:19,880 --> 01:10:21,710
不是
No.

803
01:10:21,880 --> 01:10:23,210
他们不欢迎我
I'm not welcome.

804
01:10:24,010 --> 01:10:25,220
教堂不欢迎你?
At church?

805
01:10:25,470 --> 01:10:27,550
教堂总是欢迎你的
You're always welcome at church.

806
01:10:27,760 --> 01:10:29,840
是我的儿子不欢迎我
I'm not welcome with my son.

807
01:10:31,310 --> 01:10:35,060
几年前 你们家搬来这个区前...
Years back, before you and your family moved on the block...

808
01:10:35,810 --> 01:10:37,480
我和我儿子大吵了一架
...I had an argument with my son.

809
01:10:38,270 --> 01:10:39,310
他多大了?
How old is he?

810
01:10:39,650 --> 01:10:41,190
他是大人了
He's grown up.

811
01:10:42,570 --> 01:10:47,240
我们都发了火 我说我不想再看见他了
We lost our tempers, and I said I didn't care to see him anymore.

812
01:10:47,740 --> 01:10:52,080
他也是这么说的 从那时起 我们就没讲过话了
He said the same, and we haven't spoken to each other since.

813
01:10:53,240 --> 01:10:55,500
既然你想他 干嘛不打电话给他?
If you miss him, why don't you call him?

814
01:10:56,120 --> 01:10:58,250
我害怕我要是打电话给他 他不会理我
I'm afraid if I call, he won't talk to me.

815
01:10:58,500 --> 01:11:00,000
你怎么知道?
How do you know?

816
01:11:01,000 --> 01:11:04,010
我也不知道 就是害怕他不理我
I don't know. I'm just afraid he won't.

817
01:11:04,510 --> 01:11:07,510
不是我存心冒犯你 你岁数大了 是不是不该害怕了?
No offense, but aren't you a little old to be afraid?

818
01:11:08,880 --> 01:11:11,050
人一天天变老...
You can be old for a lot of things.

819
01:11:11,260 --> 01:11:14,060
- 但总是会害怕的 - 这倒是
-  You're never too old to be afraid. -  That's true.

820
01:11:14,270 --> 01:11:16,180
我一直害怕地下室
I was afraid of our basement.

821
01:11:16,390 --> 01:11:19,690
太黑 总觉得有些怪东西在下面 里面的味道也怪怪的
It's dark. There's weird stuff down there, and it smells funny.

822
01:11:19,900 --> 01:11:23,360
这样的事烦我好多年了
That sort of thing. It's bothered me for years.

823
01:11:23,730 --> 01:11:24,900
地下室给人的感觉都是那个样子
Basements are like that.

824
01:11:26,240 --> 01:11:28,610
后来我壮着胆子下去洗衣服
I made myself go down to do some laundry...

825
01:11:28,820 --> 01:11:30,950
发觉并不那么可怕
...and I found out it's not so bad.

826
01:11:31,200 --> 01:11:35,790
开始我一直很害怕 后来把灯一打开 就什么事都没了
I worried about it, but if you turn on the lights, it's no big deal.

827
01:11:36,080 --> 01:11:37,120
你是什么意思?
What's your point?

828
01:11:37,580 --> 01:11:40,330
我的意思是 你应该打电话给你儿子
My point is, you should call your son.

829
01:11:41,290 --> 01:11:44,040
- 他要是不理我怎么办? - 至少你会知道
-  What if he won't talk to me? -  At least you'll know.

830
01:11:44,250 --> 01:11:48,630
也就不必担心这件事了 也就不会再害怕了
Then you could stop worrying about it. You won't have to be afraid anymore.

831
01:11:49,300 --> 01:11:54,350
我不管多生我爸的气 总会跟他讲话的 特别是在过节的时候
No matter how mad I was, I'd talk to my dad. Especially around the holidays.

832
01:11:56,100 --> 01:11:57,680
我不知道
I don't know.

833
01:11:57,890 --> 01:12:01,100
你试一试吧 就算是为了你的孙女
Just give it a shot. For your granddaughter anyway.

834
01:12:01,140 --> 01:12:04,230
我保证她很想你和你的礼物
I'm sure she misses you. And the presents.

835
01:12:04,940 --> 01:12:06,270
我寄过一张支票给她
I send her a check.

836
01:12:06,980 --> 01:12:10,770
我希望我爷爷奶奶也寄支票给我 他们总是寄衣服给我
I wish my grandparents did that. They always send me clothes.

837
01:12:10,780 --> 01:12:13,610
去年就给了我一件上面织着大鸟的毛衣
Last year I got a sweater with a bird knitted on it.

838
01:12:13,870 --> 01:12:14,910
啊 那不错啊
Oh, that's nice.

839
01:12:15,120 --> 01:12:17,240
二年级的男生不适合穿那个
Not for a guy in the second grade.

840
01:12:17,450 --> 01:12:20,080
要是穿了会被打的
You can get beat up for wearing something like that.

841
01:12:21,460 --> 01:12:23,500
我一个朋友 因为听说他穿过...
I have a friend who got nailed...

842
01:12:23,710 --> 01:12:26,590
有恐龙图案的睡衣 就被打了
...because there was a rumor he wore dinosaur pajamas.

843
01:12:27,710 --> 01:12:32,200
你还是赶快回家吧 想想我对你说的话
You better run home where you belong. Think about what I said.

844
01:12:32,380 --> 01:12:33,760
- 怎么样? - 好吧
-  All right? -  Okay.

845
01:12:34,550 --> 01:12:35,720
跟你聊天真高兴
It's nice talking to you.

846
01:12:36,890 --> 01:12:38,640
我也是
Nice talking to you.

847
01:12:44,900 --> 01:12:46,980
- 你怎么办? - 我?
-  What about you? -  Me?

848
01:12:47,650 --> 01:12:49,150
是 你和你儿子
Yeah. You and your son.

849
01:12:51,110 --> 01:12:52,990
再看看吧
We'll see what happens.

850
01:12:54,280 --> 01:12:55,530
圣诞快乐!
Merry Christmas.

851
01:12:56,740 --> 01:12:58,660
圣诞快乐!
Merry Christmas.

852
01:13:50,550 --> 01:13:54,170
这是我的房子 我必须保卫它!
This is my house. I have to defend it.

853
01:13:59,630 --> 01:14:02,520
战略计划图

854
01:14:26,690 --> 01:14:28,980
柏油

855
01:15:22,010 --> 01:15:25,260
先过去看看 然后回来收拾卡车
We'll check it out. We can come back for the truck.

856
01:15:33,520 --> 01:15:34,650
我们怎么进去?
How do we go in?

857
01:15:35,280 --> 01:15:38,190
到后门去 也许他会让我们进去
We'll go to the back door. Maybe he'll let us in.

858
01:15:38,400 --> 01:15:41,780
是的 他是个孩子 小孩子都傻
Yeah, he's a kid. Kids are stupid.

859
01:15:43,830 --> 01:15:47,790
感谢主赐我营养的微波炉快餐
Bless this nutritious, microwaveable macaroni and cheese dinner...

860
01:15:48,000 --> 01:15:50,790
并祝福那些低价卖东西的人们
...and the people who sold it on sale. Amen.

861
01:16:15,860 --> 01:16:18,530
就这样 现在起不再害怕
This is it. Don't get scared now.

862
01:16:31,750 --> 01:16:34,420
圣诞快乐 小子
Merry Christmas, little fella.

863
01:16:35,340 --> 01:16:40,010
我们知道你在里面 而且只有你一个人
We know that you're in there and that you're all alone.

864
01:16:40,550 --> 01:16:42,840
快点 小子 开门!
Yeah, come on, kid. Open up.

865
01:16:43,760 --> 01:16:46,390
是圣诞老人和小精灵来啦
It's Santy Claus and his elf.

866
01:16:48,850 --> 01:16:50,060
我们不会伤害你的
We won't hurt you.

867
01:16:50,730 --> 01:16:54,150
不 不会的 我们还带了礼物来给你呢
No, no. Got some nice presents for you.

868
01:16:54,480 --> 01:16:58,150
好孩子 来开门吧
Be a good little fella now and open the door.

869
01:17:02,990 --> 01:17:04,110
怎么了?
What?

870
01:17:05,950 --> 01:17:07,950
怎么了? 怎么了?
What? What?

871
01:17:08,660 --> 01:17:09,700
怎么了?
What?

872
01:17:09,870 --> 01:17:12,370
- 怎么搞的? - 抓住那...
-  What happened? -  Get that little...

873
01:17:23,880 --> 01:17:25,300
你好
Hello.

874
01:17:31,020 --> 01:17:33,390
太好了! 太好了!
Yes! Yes!

875
01:17:33,600 --> 01:17:35,100
这兔崽子有枪!
The little jerk is armed!

876
01:17:35,310 --> 01:17:39,520
好吧 我从前门进去 你从地下室进去
That's it! I'm going in the front. You go down the basement!

877
01:18:41,880 --> 01:18:44,090
自作聪明!
That smart aleck!

878
01:20:12,340 --> 01:20:16,890
这小兔崽子 死定了你
Oh, boy. That's it, you little... You little...

879
01:20:17,850 --> 01:20:20,060
这次可不会了 你这个小兔崽子
No, not this time, you little brat.

880
01:20:23,400 --> 01:20:26,270
小混蛋 你在哪?
You little creep, where are you?

881
01:20:50,220 --> 01:20:51,630
干得好!
Yes!

882
01:21:25,380 --> 01:21:27,170
我要把你的脑袋扯下来!
... rip his head off... !

883
01:21:37,050 --> 01:21:38,470
你死定了 小子
You're dead, kid.

884
01:22:25,980 --> 01:22:28,690
小浑蛋 你在哪?
Where are you, you little creep?

885
01:22:44,910 --> 01:22:47,620
哈利! 我来了
Harry, I'm coming in!

886
01:22:52,300 --> 01:22:54,340
噢 不 我真的好害怕!
Oh, no! I'm really scared.

887
01:22:54,590 --> 01:22:58,380
太晚了 小子! 我们已经在房子里 就要抓到你了!
It's too late for you, kid, we're in the house. We're gonna get you.

888
01:22:58,640 --> 01:23:00,720
好吧! 过来抓我吧!
Okay, come and get me!

889
01:23:01,100 --> 01:23:02,220
你这个...!
Why, you... !

890
01:23:08,770 --> 01:23:10,020
你死定了!
Now you're dead!

891
01:23:35,800 --> 01:23:38,300
我非杀了那小子不可!
I'm gonna kill that kid!

892
01:23:53,310 --> 01:23:55,480
- 马文 - 哈利!
-  Marv. -  Harry?

893
01:23:55,820 --> 01:23:57,570
你干嘛脱鞋?
Why'd you take your shoes off?

894
01:23:58,110 --> 01:23:59,820
你干嘛弄得像只鸡一样?
Why are you dressed like a chicken?

895
01:24:01,820 --> 01:24:05,450
我在上面 你们两个白痴 快过来抓我呀!
I'm up here, you morons. Come and get me.

896
01:24:08,620 --> 01:24:11,870
你们要投降还是要再来一点?
You guys give up, or are you thirsty for more?

897
01:24:21,720 --> 01:24:23,090
小心头!
Heads up!

898
01:24:26,180 --> 01:24:28,640
别担心 马文 我会帮你抓到他
Don't worry, Marv. I'll get him for you.

899
01:24:32,810 --> 01:24:34,480
太棒了!
Yes!

900
01:24:39,030 --> 01:24:41,320
他不过是个孩子 哈利 我们能抓到他的
He's only a kid, Harry. We can take him.

901
01:24:41,490 --> 01:24:44,570
闭嘴! 你看什么看?
Shut up, will you? What is it?

902
01:24:44,820 --> 01:24:46,950
你缺牙了
You're missing some teeth.

903
01:24:47,160 --> 01:24:49,330
是哪颗? 我的金牙!
Where? It's my gold tooth.

904
01:24:49,540 --> 01:24:52,500
我的金牙没了! 我非杀了他不可!
My gold tooth. I'll kill him. I'll kill him!

905
01:24:54,830 --> 01:24:57,040
你再用罐子打...
You bomb me with one more can, kid...

906
01:24:57,340 --> 01:25:01,510
老子一定把你的小鸡鸡扯下来放在油锅里煎!
...and I'll snap off your cojones and boil them in motor oil!

907
01:25:04,930 --> 01:25:06,050
911紧急专线
911 emergency.

908
01:25:06,260 --> 01:25:08,100
喂 有人在我家行窃
Hello, my house is being robbed.

909
01:25:08,350 --> 01:25:13,020
地址是林肯大道656号 我的名字叫墨菲
My address is 656 Lincoln Boulevard. My name is Murphy.

910
01:25:16,520 --> 01:25:17,940
不知道上面有什么东西
You never know what's there.

911
01:25:19,070 --> 01:25:20,690
他在那里!
There he is!

912
01:25:25,620 --> 01:25:27,280
抓到你了! 我抓到他了! 哈利!
I got you! I got him, Harry.

913
01:25:29,080 --> 01:25:30,370
抓到了!
I got him.

914
01:25:31,500 --> 01:25:32,790
哈利 快起来 帮我!
Harry, give me a hand!

915
01:25:36,170 --> 01:25:38,090
我抓到他了
I got him!

916
01:25:38,250 --> 01:25:39,590
哈利 帮我一把! 快起来呀!
Harry, help me. Get up!

917
01:25:41,210 --> 01:25:42,420
我抓到他了!
I got him.

918
01:26:22,130 --> 01:26:23,420
你在干嘛?
What are you doing?

919
01:26:24,260 --> 01:26:26,840
哈利 不要动!
Harry, don't move.

920
01:26:27,090 --> 01:26:28,180
马文?
Marv?

921
01:26:28,430 --> 01:26:30,760
不要动!
Don't move.

922
01:26:31,260 --> 01:26:32,810
你要干什么?
What are you doing?

923
01:26:37,560 --> 01:26:39,230
打死了吗?
Did I get him?

924
01:26:39,690 --> 01:26:41,060
打死了吗?
Did I get him?

925
01:26:41,440 --> 01:26:43,530
在哪里? 在哪里?
Where is it? Where is it?

926
01:26:43,740 --> 01:26:47,360
别管它 爽了没有? 你这个浑蛋
Never mind that. Here! How do you like it, huh? You jerk!

927
01:26:47,570 --> 01:26:50,450
快去抓那个小孩! 快去! 抓住他!
Get that kid, before I... Get that kid!

928
01:27:17,100 --> 01:27:18,390
跑哪去了?
Where'd he go?

929
01:27:19,060 --> 01:27:21,150
说不定自杀了吧
Maybe he committed suicide.

930
01:27:21,480 --> 01:27:26,280
在下面! 你们两个大坏蛋 来抓我呀 要不然我报警了!
Down here, you big horse's ass! Come get me before I call the police.

931
01:27:26,490 --> 01:27:28,490
- 我去把这小子抓来! - 等等
-  Let's get him! -  Wait, wait.

932
01:27:28,700 --> 01:27:30,570
这小子就是要我们...
It's just what he wants us to do:

933
01:27:30,780 --> 01:27:33,870
从楼下过去中他的机关! 想狠狠修理我们
Go back through his fun house so we get all tore up.

934
01:27:34,080 --> 01:27:35,620
他就要报警了!
He's gonna call the cops!

935
01:27:35,830 --> 01:27:37,500
在树屋怎么报警?
From a tree house?

936
01:27:37,750 --> 01:27:38,870
过去
Come on.

937
01:27:40,120 --> 01:27:41,710
从窗户过去?
Out the window?

938
01:27:41,880 --> 01:27:43,290
我可不行
I'm not going out the window.

939
01:27:43,500 --> 01:27:47,510
怎么? 你害怕了? 你是不是怕了?
Why, you scared? Are you afraid? Come on, get out here.

940
01:27:52,350 --> 01:27:53,680
快点啦你
Come on.

941
01:27:59,690 --> 01:28:01,190
快点啦
Come on!

942
01:28:06,820 --> 01:28:10,260
- 快点! - 哈利 还是回去吧
-  Come on. Keep going. -  Let's go back, Harry.

943
01:28:15,700 --> 01:28:16,790
马文! 别叫啦!
Shut it, Marv.

944
01:28:20,250 --> 01:28:21,290
你好!
Hey, guys!

945
01:28:21,870 --> 01:28:23,170
再看看这个!
Check this out.

946
01:28:24,250 --> 01:28:25,960
快回去! 快回去!
Go back. Go back.

947
01:29:14,470 --> 01:29:15,840
他在那里!
There he is!

948
01:29:16,010 --> 01:29:18,100
我要去报警!
Hey, I'm calling the cops!

949
01:29:19,350 --> 01:29:21,850
等等 他就是想我们跟着他
Wait, wait! He wants us to follow him.

950
01:29:22,100 --> 01:29:24,020
看我的 这边走
I got a better idea. Come on.

951
01:29:42,040 --> 01:29:43,250
嗨 兄弟
Hi, pal.

952
01:29:43,660 --> 01:29:46,920
这回栽在我们手里了吧 过来吧你
We outsmarted you this time. Get over here!

953
01:29:53,130 --> 01:29:54,300
我们怎么修理他?
What are you gonna do?

954
01:29:54,720 --> 01:29:56,760
以牙还牙
I'll do exactly what he did to us.

955
01:29:56,970 --> 01:29:58,800
我要用喷灯烧他的头!
Burn his head with a blowtorch.

956
01:29:59,010 --> 01:30:01,010
我要用熨斗烫他的脸!
I'll smash his face with an iron.

957
01:30:01,220 --> 01:30:04,060
再用油漆桶往他的脸上摔!
I'd like to slap him in the face with a paint can!

958
01:30:04,270 --> 01:30:05,890
要不就把钉子插到脚掌里去!
Shove a nail through his foot!

959
01:30:06,150 --> 01:30:11,020
把他的小嫩手指一根一根咬下来 一次咬一根
I'm gonna bite off every one of these little fingers, one at a time.

960
01:30:20,330 --> 01:30:22,700
快走 快回家去
Come on. Let's get you home.

961
01:30:45,690 --> 01:30:48,400
哇! 这下可好了!
Wow, this is great.

962
01:30:51,730 --> 01:30:54,030
做得很好 每次做案都放水
Nice move, leaving the water running.

963
01:30:54,240 --> 01:30:58,070
现在知道了 有水的房子就是你们干的
Now we know each and every house that you've hit.

964
01:31:01,530 --> 01:31:04,200
找你们两个很久了
We've been looking for you guys for a long time.

965
01:31:04,450 --> 01:31:07,330
好啊 记住了 我们就是有名的"水盗"
Yeah. Well, remember, we're the Wet Bandits.

966
01:31:07,710 --> 01:31:11,710
- 我们就是水盗 就是流水的水... - 闭嘴! 上车!
-  Wet Bandits, that's W- E- T... -  Shut up! Get in the car!

967
01:31:11,880 --> 01:31:13,500
快点!
Hey, come on. Come on.

968
01:31:14,300 --> 01:31:16,800
- 别碰我的头 朋友 - 上车!
-  Hands off the head, pal! -  Come on.

969
01:32:12,400 --> 01:32:14,310
我不是个好母亲 不是好母亲
I'm a bad parent. I'm a bad parent.

970
01:32:14,570 --> 01:32:15,770
不 你是个好母亲
No, you're not.

971
01:32:15,940 --> 01:32:18,440
你太自责了
You're beating yourself up there.

972
01:32:18,650 --> 01:32:20,360
这是常有的事
These things happen.

973
01:32:20,570 --> 01:32:24,450
要是说起不称职的父母 看看我们吧
You want to talk about bad parents? Look at us.

974
01:32:24,660 --> 01:32:29,410
我们一年中有48到49个星期在外巡回演出 几乎见不到家人
We're on the road 48, 49 weeks a year. We hardly see our families.

975
01:32:30,120 --> 01:32:32,370
那边的乔治...
Joe, over there. Gosh, you know...

976
01:32:32,580 --> 01:32:35,420
不记得自己孩子的名字
...he forgets his kids' names half the time.

977
01:32:35,630 --> 01:32:38,920
那边的兹吉根本就还没见过自己的孩子呢
Ziggy over there, he's never even met his kid.

978
01:32:39,170 --> 01:32:42,930
还有艾迪 他对不起家里的事就更多了
Eddy.... Let's just hope none of them write a book about him.

979
01:32:44,050 --> 01:32:47,560
你们有因为去度假 把孩子忘在家里吗?
Tell me, have you gone on vacation and left your child home?

980
01:32:50,980 --> 01:32:52,350
没有
No.

981
01:32:53,150 --> 01:32:56,020
但是我倒是有一次把孩子忘在殡仪馆了
But I did leave one at a funeral parlor once.

982
01:32:56,860 --> 01:33:00,110
那也是同样让人很难受
Yeah, it was terrible too. I was all distraught and everything.

983
01:33:00,320 --> 01:33:04,570
我和我太太把孩子留在殡仪馆了
The wife and I, we left the little tyke there in the funeral parlor.

984
01:33:04,820 --> 01:33:08,490
孩子被忘在殡仪馆里整整一天 到了晚上...
All day. You know, we went back at night, when we...

985
01:33:08,700 --> 01:33:10,950
才想起他来 我们赶紧去找他
...came to our senses, there he was.

986
01:33:11,210 --> 01:33:14,330
他在遗体旁待了整整一天
Apparently, he was there all day with a corpse.

987
01:33:15,380 --> 01:33:18,670
六七个星期之后 他就好了 你知道的...
He was okay. You know, after six, seven weeks.

988
01:33:18,880 --> 01:33:21,340
就又说又蹦又跳了
He came around and started talking again.

989
01:33:22,720 --> 01:33:25,720
小孩子很快就恢复了 不像大人那样
They get over it. Kids are resilient like that.

990
01:33:25,930 --> 01:33:27,640
我们或许不应该谈论这个话题
We shouldn't talk about this.

991
01:33:27,890 --> 01:33:32,320
- 我只是想让你振作起来 - 对不起
-  I was just trying to cheer you up. -  I'm sorry I did.

992
01:33:58,290 --> 01:33:59,420
妈!
Mom?

993
01:34:04,590 --> 01:34:05,880
妈!
Mom?

994
01:34:09,930 --> 01:34:11,970
妈?
Mom?

995
01:34:58,310 --> 01:34:59,650
凯文!
Kevin!

996
01:35:01,190 --> 01:35:02,320
凯文!
Kevin!

997
01:35:33,680 --> 01:35:35,560
圣诞快乐! 宝贝
Merry Christmas, sweetheart.

998
01:35:44,980 --> 01:35:47,490
凯文 妈妈真的对不起你
Oh, Kevin, I'm so sorry.

999
01:36:07,420 --> 01:36:09,220
其他人都去哪了?
Where's everybody else?

1000
01:36:09,930 --> 01:36:11,930
噢 他们回不来
Oh, baby, they couldn't come.

1001
01:36:12,140 --> 01:36:13,390
他们是想回来的...
They wanted to so much...

1002
01:36:13,600 --> 01:36:18,060
我才没有流口水呢! 有吗?
I didn't fall asleep in the back and drool all over you, did I?

1003
01:36:18,270 --> 01:36:20,600
- 你流了 - 别吵了
-  You do drool! -  Shut up!

1004
01:36:23,440 --> 01:36:27,070
凯文 你还好吧?
Kevin, my boy. How are you? It's good to see you.

1005
01:36:27,280 --> 01:36:29,030
你没事吧
You're all right.

1006
01:36:29,530 --> 01:36:30,740
我爱你 你还好吗?
I love you. You okay?

1007
01:36:32,410 --> 01:36:33,530
凯文
Hey, Kev.

1008
01:36:35,870 --> 01:36:38,540
你还没把房子给烧了 真是了不起
It's cool that you didn't burn the place down.

1009
01:36:40,870 --> 01:36:42,330
谢谢 巴兹
Thanks, Buzz.

1010
01:36:44,040 --> 01:36:46,040
等一下 你们是怎么回来的?
Wait a minute. How'd you guys get home?

1011
01:36:46,250 --> 01:36:48,760
我们坐的是你不愿意等的那班飞机
On the morning flight you didn't want to wait for.

1012
01:36:48,960 --> 01:36:52,220
- 喔! 谢谢 - 圣诞快乐!
-  Oh, no. Thank you. -  Merry Christmas.

1013
01:36:52,430 --> 01:36:53,840
圣诞快乐!
Merry Christmas.

1014
01:36:54,470 --> 01:36:56,550
谁去找间开门的商店
Someone has to find an open store.

1015
01:36:56,760 --> 01:36:58,390
我昨天去店里买了
I went shopping yesterday.

1016
01:37:01,060 --> 01:37:02,600
你? 买东西?
You, shopping?

1017
01:37:02,900 --> 01:37:05,610
我买了牛奶 买了鸡蛋 还有柔软精
I got some milk, eggs and fabric softener.

1018
01:37:07,570 --> 01:37:09,440
- 什么? - 真的假的?
-  What? -  No kidding?

1019
01:37:09,650 --> 01:37:11,360
这孩子还真好玩
What a funny guy.

1020
01:37:11,570 --> 01:37:13,700
我们不在家的时候你还做了什么?
What else did you do while we were away?

